query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stats')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('bayesian',
'classification',
'correlation',
'distributions',
'hypothesis-testing',
'machine-learning',
'mathematical-statistics',
'neural-networks',
'probability',
'regression',
'self-study',
'time-series');
